Text: Disc is the same disk from v. 8.0 up until this release, maybe even longer.

It's 2010 and we're still haunted by the ghost of win XP! 

Whenever I try to generate my activation code I get a error message about my mac addy, and I can find it @ "C:\document and setting\All Users\Application Data\e-onsoftware\Vue 8 xStream.reg." 

Seeing that I'm running win7 64, this bit of info is useless to me. Thanks for the upload, but it looks like I'll have to delete this prog...

Thanks again for your hard work! Merry holidays!  (^_-)
